Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,籠中鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的口袋本好像也收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:21:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就是中央種子島高中機器人研究部的各位嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點突然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我有件事情想要告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我們走一趟嗎

